getCommitSize

public int getCommitSize(SDLoaderParams lps)
Get the commit size for this node, if this node is not a driver node then get the commit size of the driver root node. based on following precedence: 1. command line param 2. AM custom property for only for the driver root node 3. environment variable 4. default value

Parameters:
lps - SDLoaderParams
Returns:
int commit size to use for loader

getDefaultConflictBumpStrategy

public SDAltKeyBumpStrategy getDefaultConflictBumpStrategy(java.lang.String attr,
                                                           oracle.jbo.server.ViewRowImpl row)
Method returns default conflict strategy. Checks if the failing attribute is a part of any of the unique key validators. If yes, then find out the attribute belonging to the index which can be bumped. Create a new bump strategy and return. Nu Return null in case unable to find any default bumping strategy, if failing attribute doesn't belong to an index or , index doesn't contain any translatable attribute which is safe to be bumped. Default conflict resolution strategy is to bump incoming ORACLE record values.

Parameters:
attr -
row -
Returns:
